'''Yennayer''' d-ass amezwaru n useggwas n taswast ufellaḥt yetseqdacen [[Imaziɣen]] seg taglest deg akkw [[Tafriqt n Ugafa]]. Yeɛdel s wass amezwaru n [[Yennayer (aggur)|yennayer]] n [[Taswast tayulyant]], yesɛan ass-agi asekḥer n 13 ussan s wassaɣ ɣer [[Taswast tagriguryant]], ihi ass n [[14 yennayer]] n yal aseggwas. Seg tuccḍa n tiddukliwin tidelsanin timezwura yebɣan tuqqla ar tameɣra tamensayt agi, tettwaggzenen ar ungar, turda n azmez amensay d [[12 yennayer]] tecaɛ aṭas, ladɣa di [[Lezzayer]].
